headline: Aflac (NYSE:AFL) Reports Sharp Drop in Q1 Earnings but Dividends Remain Stable
summary: Aflac (NYSE:AFL) has recently reported significant declines in its first quarter earnings, with net income and EPS from continuing operations both dropping substantially compared to the previous year. Despite this, the company's stock price remained relatively flat over the last quarter, gaining just 0.40%.
